00:08:27.246 --> 00:08:28.296
They don't need any kind of

00:08:28.296 --> 00:08:29.236
instructions.

00:08:29.236 --> 00:08:30.876
They don't need anything to tell

00:08:30.876 --> 00:08:31.576
them to do that.

00:08:32.086 --> 00:08:33.385
So, don't make them sit through

00:08:33.385 --> 00:08:34.506
