00:29:44.986 --> 00:29:45.806
So, if you want to build a

00:29:45.806 --> 00:29:47.916
one-handed AR experience, you're

00:29:47.916 --> 00:29:48.786
going to need to use really

00:29:48.786 --> 00:29:50.356
reachable controls that are

00:29:50.456 --> 00:29:52.026
really easy to access.

00:29:52.496 --> 00:29:55.536
So, an example of that is

00:29:55.536 --> 00:29:55.936
