00:30:04.696 --> 00:30:05.566
reachable spot.

00:30:05.946 --> 00:30:07.086
So, even while you're using one

00:30:07.086 --> 00:30:09.026
hand to focus the reticle on the

00:30:09.026 --> 00:30:10.946
center of the screen, to

00:30:10.946 --> 00:30:11.906
