00:30:15.046 --> 00:30:16.716
button to easily add your

00:30:16.716 --> 00:30:17.846
measurements, to easily place

00:30:17.846 --> 00:30:18.436
those points.

00:30:19.576 --> 00:30:22.096
So, using indirect controls can

00:30:22.096 --> 00:30:24.026
be a great way to make it not

00:30:24.026 --> 00:30:25.846
only easy to use AR experiences,

00:30:25.946 --> 00:30:31.286
but one-handed ones as well.

00:30:31.496 --> 00:30:33.196
Alright. So, that's how to pick

